

# Installation Guide

## 1. Copy module

Place the file:

TenvisJPT3815W.pm

into:

/usr/share/perl5/ZoneMinder/Control/


## 2. Set authentication

Edit the file and replace:

PUT_YOUR_BASE64_HERE

with your own credentials encoded in base64.

## 3. Configure ZoneMinder

### Create Control Type

Name: TenvisJPT3815W  
Protocol: TenvisJPT3815W  
Type: Local

Enable:

- Can Move  
- Can Move Continuous  
- Can Pan  
- Can Tilt

### In Monitor

Control Address:

192.168.x.x

(no http, no user/pass)

## 4. Restart

sudo systemctl restart zoneminder


## 5. Test

Use arrows in ZoneMinder interface.  
Camera should stop when button is released.
